window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>This omnibus contains the first three novels of the Frith Chronicles, all of which are also sold separately:</p> <p></p> <ul> <li>Book 1: <i>Knightmare Arcanist</i></li> <li>Book 2:<i> Dread Pirate Arcanist</i></li> <li>Book 3: <i>Coliseum Arcanist</i></li> </ul> <p>Volke Savan has always wanted to be an arcanist - someone who has bonded with a mystical creature and is capable of wielding magic. Phoenix arcanists can create fire and heal, hydra arcanists can create poison and recover from most injuries, and knightmare arcanists are masters of shadow and fear.</p> <p>After bonding with a mystical creature, Volke travels to the mainland, fighting through pirates, tournaments, and dastardly scoundrels, all to follow in the footsteps of legendary swashbucklers and heroes alike.</p>"; 
